&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User Story:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Customer&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;br&gt;
I want to report a dispute through a conversational chatbot,&lt;br&gt;
So that I can get guided assistance through the submission process.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Acceptance Criteria:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given&lt;/strong&gt; I initiate a dispute conversation with the chatbot&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;When&lt;/strong&gt; I interact with the AI agent&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Then&lt;/strong&gt; the following experience is provided:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Natural language understanding of dispute description&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guided question flow to gather required information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transaction lookup and selection via conversation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document upload prompts when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clarifying questions based on dispute type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Summary and confirmation before submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;And&lt;/strong&gt; chatbot leverages Vertex AI Agent Engine&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;And&lt;/strong&gt; conversation history is logged for audit&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;And&lt;/strong&gt; escalation to human agent available if needed&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;And&lt;/strong&gt; completed dispute matches data model requirements&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prerequisites:&lt;/strong&gt; Epic 1 Feature 1.2 (Vertex AI), Feature 1.3 (data models)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Notes:&lt;/strong&gt; Use Vertex AI Agent Engine with custom intents for dispute submission. Implement context management for multi-turn conversations. Integrate with transaction API for lookup. Provide fallback to human agent.&lt;/p&gt;
